purpose: The email announces the Call for Papers for the ACM/IEEE International Symposium on Code Generation and Optimization (CGO 2026), which will be held in Sydney, Australia. It provides details about the submission deadlines, including the paper submission date of May 29, 2025, the author rebuttal period from July 8 to July 10, 2025, and the paper notification date of July 21, 2025. The email encourages researchers and practitioners in the field of optimization and code generation techniques to submit their work.
